	(46474,1610,'quote_or_personal_detail_ml_rich_text_basic_english','Ekpar speaks sign language and has done fundraising for sign language education, especially for children. He also created a media platform, Bagdax, that offered opportunities for artists and featured events open to everybody. \nHe loves dancing, playing tennis and football. “People would call him Roberto Baggio as he was really good at playing football!” his sister added during the interview. \nShe also mentioned that Ekpar is very charismatic but humble – “a person with a beautiful character and integrity”.\n'),
