	(46994,1614,'quote_or_personal_detail_ml_rich_text_basic_english','Mamat is married and has a daughter. His brother described him as sociable and helpful: “He liked to move around to help people; people are always calling him.” Mamat is a very active person and does not like to stay indoors for long.  \nThe husband of Mamat’s niece, [Akber Hushur](#case- SR028), is also in prison with a 17 years’ sentence.'),
