	(47124,1615,'quote_or_personal_detail_ml_rich_text_basic_english','Abduhalik is a writer and a publisher of more than 30 articles. He opened the biggest bookshop in the county and organized book-related events and activities. His work was all about preserving Uyghur traditions and culture. He always respected the restrictions and policies imposed by the Chinese authorities, and he was never hostile to the system, according to his brother.\nAbduhalik is married and has two children.'),
