	(47514,1618,'quote_or_personal_detail_ml_rich_text_basic_english','Rifat, a government official at the time of his arrest, studied geology and collected precious stones. He had planned to start an amber business with his brother-in-law. \nHe has a son and a daughter. Before his detention, he had planned to leave China with his family but that did not happen because the passport for his son was never issued by the Chinese authorities and Rifat and his wife did not want to leave any of their children behind.'),
