	(48424,1625,'quote_or_personal_detail_ml_rich_text_basic_english','His father describes Imamhusen and his twin brother, Imamhesen, as very smart and good at school, mature despite their young age and interested in sport. He also remembers how close they were to him when he was still living in Xinjiang. He said: “They used to be my boys, we were really close to each other. We used to go to the restaurants... They had a lot of appetite! They put their hands straight into the pot, they had crazy appetite.” He ended the interview saying: “I just want … to see them again.” Unfortunately, Imamhusen and Imamhesen’s mother, [Nurmangul Ebey](#case-SR018), was reportedly detained in September 2016.'),
