	(49072,1630,'summary',''),
	(49073,1630,'_summary','field_6037389d32918'),
	(49074,1630,'quote_or_personal_detail_ml_rich_text_basic_english','His uncle remembers Akber as very religious. “He never missed a prayer,” he added. \nAkber is married and has three daughters and one son. According to the last information that Abker’s uncle has from December 2019, Akber’s wife was sent to an internment camp in November 2017, later released and sent in January 2019 to work for a textile company far from where their children live, and only allowed to return home once every 50 days. \nUnfortunately, the brother of Akber’s uncle, [Mamat Ablat](#case-SR11), is also in prison with a 16–17-year sentence.'),
